    "client_msg_id": "92c0ac71-a9b7-4f65-bce2-84d4439da23b",
    "text": "You can't control routing yet. Though you don't have to go through a router. The goal is to be able to make your own components with a little \"language\" (ideally not requiring a bunch of typing). And from that you should be able to have quite a be able to create many different routing options.\n\nFor real orchestration, yet I have thought about it. I actually don't think it is too hard. Just component types that allow input through the real world and output. Ideas aren't fully fleshed out. It is definitely not designed right now for real world data and its complexity. But definitely not impossible.",
